00:57.530 --> 00:58.700
<b>It is.</b>

00:58.700 --> 01:02.120
<b>But it's not one that we can abandon lightly.</b>

01:02.120 --> 01:03.410
<b>Akame...</b>

01:03.410 --> 01:07.670
<b>If we throw in the towel here, 
the dead won't be able to rest in peace.</b>

01:09.460 --> 01:10.880
<b>You're right.</b>

01:12.210 --> 01:15.090
<b>We have to put an end to the suffering.</b>

01:24.850 --> 01:28.900
<b><i>My life was the price to use Susanoo's hidden ability.</i></b>

01:29.440 --> 01:31.440
<b><i>And yet I'm still alive.</i></b>

01:32.030 --> 01:37.450
<b><i>Susanoo, you gave your own life to save mine.</i></b>

01:42.790 --> 01:45.160
<b><i>You weren't simply a Relic.</i></b>

01:45.790 --> 01:49.670
<b><i>You were my valued partner.</i></b>

01:53.380 --> 01:57.550
<b><i>You told me that you wanted 
to come out of this revolution on top</i></b>

01:57.550 --> 02:00.180
