<b>What did you say, you bastard?</b>

03:57.090 --> 03:57.710
<b>Stop!</b>

03:59.880 --> 04:00.840
<b>Damn it!</b>

04:01.340 --> 04:04.220
<b>How long are we supposed to keep this up?</b>

04:04.220 --> 04:07.350
<b>This nation won't last much longer.</b>

04:07.890 --> 04:12.060
<b>Most of the civilians we're supposed to protect have sided with the rebel army.</b>

04:12.060 --> 04:14.810
<b>Are we really okay with this as the Jaegers?!</b>

04:14.810 --> 04:16.310
<b>Please calm down.</b>

04:17.270 --> 04:20.030
<b>It's likely that this unrest will persist after the revolution.</b>

04:20.650 --> 04:23.740
<b>We will be needed then.</b>

04:23.740 --> 04:26.700
<b>You talk as though you knew all this would happen.</b>

04:27.370 --> 04:29.580
<b>It took place faster than I'd anticipated, though.</b>

04:29.580 --> 04:30.910
<b>Huh?</b>

04:30.910 --> 04:33.290
<b>I've long hoped for revolution.{allow me to arbitrarily reveal to you my secret plans}</b>

04:33.290 --> 04:37.210
<b>I joined the Jaegers in order to change this nation from the inside.</b>

04:37.840 --> 04:39.670
<b>Change the nation?</b>

04:39.670 --> 04:42.010
<b>This empire is rotten to the core.</b>

04:42.010 --> 04:45.380
<b>However, it would have been foolish to openly rebel like those out there.</b>

04:45.380 --> 04:48.050
<b>That's why you joined Esdeath's special forces.</b>

04:48.050 --> 04:48.850
<b>That's right.</b>

04:49.560 --> 04:51.220
<b>She's quite the interesting specimen.</b>

04:52.020 --> 04:53.310
<b>You're a strange guy.</b>

04:53.940 --> 04:55.020
<b>I get that a lot.</b>

04:55.770 --> 05:01.400
<b>I got so comfortable here that 
I almost forgot my true objective.</b>

05:07.740 --> 05:10.910
<b>So what will you do?</b>

05:10.910 --> 05:12.450
<b>You don't have much time left.</b>

05:14.290 --> 05:17.000
<b>Y-You knew about Kurome's condition?</b>

05:17.000 --> 05:18.840
<b>Don't look so surprised.</b>

05:19.540 --> 05:22.090
<b>Your attitude and behavior gave it away.</b>

05:24.970 --> 05:27.970
<b>If you escape now, you won't have to worry about them coming after you.</b>

05:27.970 --> 05:29.550
<b>You can be free.</b>

05:30.140 --> 05:31.680
<b>Free...</b>

05:31.680 --> 05:32.390
<b>That's right.</b>

05:33.270 --> 05:35.940
<b>A taste of freedom isn't what I desire.</b>

05:36.730 --> 05:39.440
<b>There's only one thing I want.</b>

05:43.990 --> 05:46.990
<b>Truly, this is how a battle should be.</b>

05:46.990 --> 05:50.160
<b>If you're discontent with your lot in life,</b>

05:50.160 --> 05:52.990
<b>prove your strength by defeating me!</b>

05:52.990 --> 05:55.000
<b>Say your prayers, Esdeath!</b>

05:55.000 --> 05:57.750
<b>If we bring you down, this will all be over!</b>

05:59.380 --> 06:00.710
<b>A Relic-wielder.</b>

06:00.710 --> 06:01.630
<b>How interesting!</b>

06:10.970 --> 06:13.720
<b>Is there none here who can overcome death?</b>

06:15.270 --> 06:17.180
<b><i>Tatsumi survived.</i></b>

06:17.180 --> 06:19.810
<b><i>He managed to escape death, even in mortal peril.</i></b>

06:19.810 --> 06:22.480
<b><i>I knew that we were destined for each other.</i></b>

06:24.940 --> 06:26.530
<b><i>Wait for me.</i></b>

06:26.530 --> 06:29.530
<b><i>After I take care of these weaklings, I'll see you again.</i></b>

06:29.860 --> 06:32.700
<b>Shisuikan and Bench Fortress have both fallen.</b>

06:32.700 --> 06:35.790
<b>The capital's almost completely surrounded.</b>

06:35.790 --> 06:37.500
<b>What is Esdeath doing?</b>

06:37.500 --> 06:42.840
<b>Not even the general could 
fend off an attack from all sides!</b>

06:42.840 --> 06:43.960
<b>Your Majesty!</b>

06:44.920 --> 06:48.510
<b>Will this nation fall on my account?</b>

06:49.470 --> 06:51.180
<b>Have I followed the wrong path?</b>

06:51.180 --> 06:54.600
<b>Not at all, Your Majesty.</b>

06:54.600 --> 06:55.930
<b>H-Honest...</b>

06:56.560 --> 06:58.890
<b>Not one person here can be depended on.</b>

06:59.890 --> 07:01.770
<b>Everyone is far too flustered.</b>

07:02.730 --> 07:07.530
<b>I am painfully aware of how you are feeling, Your Majesty.</b>

07:07.530 --> 07:09.780
<b>The citizens are being foolish.</b>

07:09.780 --> 07:14.830
<b>They don't understand what it's like 
to protect an entire empire.{well...ok}</b>

07:14.830 --> 07:17.620
<b>I can't believe my people would rebel.</b>

07:17.620 --> 07:18.910
<b>What am I supposed to do?</b>

07:19.830 --> 07:24.170
<b>Your Majesty, at times, an emperor must be firm.</b>

07:24.790 --> 07:28.550
<b>Now is the time to demonstrate your authority.</b>

07:29.050 --> 07:30.550
<b>Prepare our trump card at once!</b>

07:34.010 --> 07:36.760
<b><i>The emperor's true power...</i></b>

07:41.940 --> 07:44.190
<b>This is the end for me.</b>

07:44.860 --> 07:45.400
<b>So...</b>

07:46.440 --> 07:49.320
<b>Let's settle this once and for all, Sis.</b>

07:51.320 --> 07:53.360
<b>They say these were Revolutionary Army spies.</b>

07:53.740 --> 07:55.570
<b>Is this meant as a warning?</b>

07:55.570 --> 07:56.950
<b>How cruel.</b>

08:00.960 --> 08:02.420
<b>It's a code.</b>

08:03.460 --> 08:04.460
<b>A code?</b>

08:05.040 --> 08:06.920
<b>A message for me.</b>

08:07.630 --> 08:08.380
<b>What was that?</b>

08:09.590 --> 08:12.800
<b>"I will be waiting for you 
near the Kadai Forest facility."</b>

08:12.800 --> 08:15.180
<b>Don't be stupid. You know it's a trap!</b>

08:15.930 --> 08:18.810
<b>The empire would have no reason to single me out at this point.</b>

08:19.430 --> 08:20.850
<b>This is a personal challenge.</b>

08:21.310 --> 08:23.100
<b>A personal challenge? From whom?</b>

08:24.310 --> 08:26.360
<b>Kurome wants to settle things for good.</b>

08:28.070 --> 08:32.150
<b>Is it important that you two see this through?</b>

08:33.700 --> 08:37.870
<b>Even considering how many people are pinning their hopes on us?</b>

08:37.870 --> 08:40.410
<b>Do you really have to do this?</b>

08:40.910 --> 08:42.830
<b>That's even more reason to.{i have no idea why but ok}</b>

08:43.370 --> 08:46.920
<b>I have to respect Kurome's wishes.</b>

08:46.920 --> 08:48.540
<b>Even if she's the enemy?</b>

08:48.540 --> 08:49.630
<b>She's my sister.</b>

08:51.260 --> 08:55.630
<b>I'm the only one who can understand and accept her wishes.</b>

08:58.510 --> 09:01.310
<b>I understand. I'm coming with you.</b>

09:01.310 --> 09:02.480
<b>No, you're not.</b>

09:02.480 --> 09:05.600
<b>We'll need your strength in the final battle.</b>

09:06.230 --> 09:07.560
<b>You must fulfill your mission.</b>

09:07.560 --> 09:08.150
<b>Then...</b>

09:08.150 --> 09:10.440
<b>Promise me you'll come back alive!</b>

09:11.650 --> 09:13.110
<b>Tatsumi...</b>

09:13.110 --> 09:15.150
<b>That's what you've always asked me, right?</b>

09:15.530 --> 09:17.030
<b>The least you can do is promise me the same!</b>

09:19.240 --> 09:20.240
<b>Okay.</b>

09:21.540 --> 09:22.540
<b>It's a promise.</b>

09:53.440 --> 09:56.740
<b>I knew you wouldn't let me down, Sis.</b>

09:59.740 --> 10:01.080
<b>Kurome...</b>

10:02.790 --> 10:03.790
<b>Would you like some?</b>

10:16.800 --> 10:20.220
<b>This is where we were once reunited.</b>

10:21.140 --> 10:25.180
<b>And this is also the place where you betrayed us.</b>

10:26.310 --> 10:29.810
<b>I can't think of a more fitting place for me to kill you.</b>

10:30.480 --> 10:32.060
<b>This takes me back.</b>

10:32.980 --> 10:36.190
<b>You were always the one who protected me.</b>

10:37.650 --> 10:42.580
<b>As orphans, we had no other home but here.</b>

10:44.080 --> 10:46.620
<b>Raised as assassins for the empire,</b>

10:47.080 --> 10:52.330
<b>our purpose in life was to maintain public order by eliminating any potential insurgency.</b>

10:52.330 --> 10:54.920
<b>That is what we were told and how we were raised.</b>

10:56.090 --> 10:58.130
<b>We obeyed our orders,</b>

10:58.130 --> 11:00.720
<b>killing those who had wronged the empire,</b>

11:03.720 --> 11:06.680
<b>because we believed it was the right thing to do.</b>

11:09.230 --> 11:10.850
<b>Sis!</b>

11:12.480 --> 11:13.400
<b>Kurome.</b>

11:14.060 --> 11:15.400
<b>Sis...</b>

11:18.150 --> 11:23.280
<b>After being trained in separate divisions, 
we were finally reunited—</b>

11:23.990 --> 11:26.740
<b>simply because we were needed to replace fallen comrades.</b>

11:29.120 --> 11:32.370
<b>We were inseparable after that.</b>

11:32.370 --> 11:35.130
<b>It was as if we were reliving our childhood.</b>

11:35.920 --> 11:39.050
<b>We were the most skilled assassination unit the empire had known.</b>

11:39.550 --> 11:41.880
<b>Some missions were difficult,</b>

11:41.880 --> 11:44.090
<b>but we were able to rely on each other and pull through.</b>

11:44.090 --> 11:47.470
<b>As long as I was with you, I was happy.</b>

11:47.470 --> 11:48.600
<b>But you...</b>

11:49.390 --> 11:50.350
<b>But you...</b>

11:51.190 --> 11:52.190
<b>But you...</b>

11:56.690 --> 12:00.360
<b>You betrayed the empire and joined Night Raid!</b>

12:00.950 --> 12:02.200
<b>Why?</b>

12:02.200 --> 12:03.860
<b>I tried to stop you.</b>

12:08.290 --> 12:12.000
<b>After you left me, I was miserable.</b>

12:12.000 --> 12:13.790
<b>I thought about you every day.</b>

12:13.790 --> 12:15.750
<b>About how I was going to kill you.</b>

12:16.540 --> 12:18.340
<b>If you do, will you find peace?</b>

12:18.710 --> 12:20.710
<b>I will never know peace.</b>

12:20.710 --> 12:22.050
<b>I just want to be the one to do it.</b>

12:22.760 --> 12:25.890
<b>So that you'll belong to me.</b>

12:29.310 --> 12:32.560
<b>Using your Imperial Relic takes an enormous amount of energy.</b>

12:32.980 --> 12:35.100
<b>It must be agonizing in your condition.</b>

12:35.650 --> 12:36.810
<b>I'll make the pain go away.</b>

12:38.770 --> 12:40.440
<b>Let's kill each other,</b>

12:40.940 --> 12:42.280
<b>Sis.{end of part a}</b>

12:43.110 --> 12:45.990
Kurome's

12:43.110 --> 12:45.990
