12:44.610 --> 12:45.990
<b>Kurome...</b>

12:47.160 --> 12:49.240
<b>She went out, didn't she?</b>

12:49.910 --> 12:52.500
<b>To settle everything for herself.</b>

12:53.370 --> 12:56.420
<b>Why would she do that without telling us?</b>

12:56.420 --> 12:58.790
<b>Because you would have stopped her.</b>

13:01.300 --> 13:03.670
<b>Do you have any idea where she'd go?</b>

13:03.670 --> 13:05.720
<b>Maybe a place that's special to them?</b>

13:28.200 --> 13:30.580
<b>Why did you betray our squad?</b>

13:30.580 --> 13:33.620
<b>We could've stayed together!</b>

13:33.620 --> 13:38.130
<b>I started to realize that what we were doing wasn't to keep the peace.</b>

13:38.130 --> 13:39.000
<b>It was all a lie!</b>

13:40.000 --> 13:45.300
<b>We were a special unit that executed missions from the capital, no matter what they were.</b>

13:45.300 --> 13:49.350
<b>If the current empire continues to exist, the citizens are doomed to suffer.</b>

13:49.350 --> 13:51.640
<b>That's why I tried to get you to escape with me.</b>

13:51.640 --> 13:53.350
<b>I couldn't just run away.</b>

13:53.350 --> 13:56.520
<b>Our comrades gave their lives for our cause! 
How could I betray them?</b>

13:56.520 --> 13:59.190
<b>The rulers of the empire are the source of all this misery.</b>

13:59.190 --> 14:02.020
<b>If eliminating them will help the citizens,</b>

14:02.020 --> 14:03.860
<b>I'm sure our fallen comrades would understand.</b>

14:03.860 --> 14:05.440
<b>You don't get to decide that, Sis!</b>

14:21.960 --> 14:23.420
<b>A Danger Beast?</b>

14:23.420 --> 14:24.960
<b>An experimental subject entombed here.</b>

14:25.340 --> 14:27.970
<b>Our battle must have awakened it.</b>

14:30.550 --> 14:31.140
<b>Kurome!</b>

14:35.350 --> 14:36.560
<b>Natala!</b>

14:39.310 --> 14:41.650
<b>How dare you do that to my friend?</b>

14:42.360 --> 14:43.190
<b>Doya!</b>

14:49.570 --> 14:50.660
<b>Doya!{that wasn't very clever at all}</b>

14:52.240 --> 14:53.660
<b>Doya too...</b>

14:53.660 --> 14:56.410
<b>I'll never accept you into my collection!</b>

15:06.840 --> 15:08.800
<b>Are you all right, Kurome?</b>

15:09.430 --> 15:10.380
<b>Sis...</b>

15:13.390 --> 15:13.890
<b>Let's do it.</b>

15:34.950 --> 15:36.080
<b>Eliminate!</b>

15:48.130 --> 15:50.590
<b>We haven't lost our touch, have we?</b>

15:51.220 --> 15:54.800
<b>Nothing can stop us when we're together.</b>

15:54.800 --> 15:56.760
<b>Isn't that right, Sis?</b>

16:07.570 --> 16:08.690
<b>Come forth!</b>

16:22.750 --> 16:25.460
<b>So a few no-name puppets won't do, huh?</b>

16:25.460 --> 16:27.880
<b>This is the end!</b>

16:34.260 --> 16:36.640
<b>I won't let you hurt Kurome.</b>

16:36.640 --> 16:37.640
<b>Wave?</b>

16:37.640 --> 16:38.930
<b>Night Raid...</b>

16:38.930 --> 16:40.060
<b>I'll take you on!</b>

16:42.480 --> 16:42.940
<b>Tatsumi?</b>

16:46.230 --> 16:47.480
<b>Get out of the way, Tatsumi!</b>

16:47.480 --> 16:49.110
<b>Don't interrupt us!</b>

16:49.900 --> 16:53.650
<b>Kurome, I can't just abandon one of my comrades.</b>

16:53.650 --> 16:55.240
<b>This isn't what I wanted.</b>

16:55.990 --> 16:57.200
<b>Kurome...</b>

16:57.200 --> 16:59.410
<b>Tatsumi, why are you here?</b>

16:59.410 --> 17:02.000
<b>To make sure no one interferes with your duel.</b>

17:05.040 --> 17:07.540
<b>Tatsumi, I don't have time to deal with—</b>

17:07.540 --> 17:09.040
<b>I want to stop them too!</b>

17:09.040 --> 17:12.170
<b>But if I do, they'll never overcome their past!</b>

17:12.170 --> 17:15.260
<b>Is that what you've learned from Night Raid?</b>

17:15.260 --> 17:17.550
<b>I can't allow this battle to occur!</b>

17:17.550 --> 17:19.560
<b>Everyone has their own reasons to fight!</b>

17:19.560 --> 17:24.140
<b>Sometimes, you have to settle it yourself 
or there's no way forward!</b>

17:28.860 --> 17:30.770
<b>Their own reasons to fight...</b>

17:37.660 --> 17:38.700
<b>I...</b>

17:41.410 --> 17:42.410
<b>Wave.</b>

17:46.870 --> 17:48.790
<b>Thank you for coming.</b>

17:49.670 --> 17:53.130
<b>I wish we could've gotten closer under different circumstances.</b>

17:57.050 --> 17:58.180
<b>Kurome...</b>

17:58.680 --> 18:02.560
<b>I have to sort out my regrets from back then.</b>

18:03.770 --> 18:05.770
<b>So that I can finally move on.</b>

18:06.560 --> 18:08.400
<b>Let's do this, Sis.</b>

18:17.950 --> 18:20.870
<b>Kurome... My little sister...</b>

18:22.580 --> 18:26.500
<b>Yeah. I love you, Sis.</b>

19:17.960 --> 19:20.930
<b>Was there no other way?{passionate yuri incest hatesex}</b>

19:24.640 --> 19:28.310
<b>I couldn't do anything for Kurome.</b>

19:29.480 --> 19:32.020
<b>You came here for her.</b>

19:33.110 --> 19:34.310
<b>That's plenty.</b>

19:39.070 --> 19:40.150
<b>Damn it.</b>

19:41.030 --> 19:42.450
<b>Damn it...</b>

19:43.070 --> 19:44.990
<b>Damn it!</b>

19:51.370 --> 19:52.710
<b>Night Raid...</b>

19:53.670 --> 19:56.040
<b>What are we fighting for?</b>

19:56.670 --> 20:00.970
<b>If you can't answer that for yourself, 
you have no business holding a weapon.</b>

20:00.970 --> 20:05.640
<b>Only those who have steeled themselves have the right to wield a blade.{I like it}</b>

20:06.350 --> 20:07.310
<b>Steeled?</b>

20:08.100 --> 20:10.060
<b>Steeled themselves to carry on, no matter what.</b>

20:26.530 --> 20:27.410
<b>Akame!</b>

20:28.950 --> 20:30.660
<b>I told you not to come after me.</b>

20:31.500 --> 20:33.000
<b>I didn't come to fight.</b>

20:33.460 --> 20:37.000
<b>Just to pick up a wounded comrade.</b>

20:41.420 --> 20:44.300
<b>I've lost so many things that are important to me.</b>

20:45.180 --> 20:46.600
<b>But you...</b>

20:46.600 --> 20:51.810
<b>You've been through more than I could ever imagine.</b>

20:54.020 --> 20:58.480
<b>Akame, we're done losing things that are precious to us.</b>

21:26.300 --> 21:28.760
<b>What impressive determination.</b>

21:28.760 --> 21:31.470
<b>Your wisdom is a testament to your greatness.</b>

21:31.470 --> 21:37.480
<b>Now is the time to unleash the capital's 
ultimate Imperial Relic.</b>

21:38.020 --> 21:45.070
<b>Demonstrate your true power to those fools—
rebels and citizens alike.</b>

21:45.740 --> 21:48.160
<b>I am the emperor.</b>

21:48.660 --> 21:52.700
